title: "Fanny Buitrago - Grass Symphony"
date: 2024-12-30 12:00:00 -0000
author: Fanny Buitrago
quote: "Seas of grass sway in harmony,"
subject: Modern Nature Poetry in South America
permalink: /Modern Nature Poetry in South America/Fanny Buitrago/Fanny Buitrago - Grass Symphony
---

Seas of grass sway in harmony,
A whisper, a gentle decree,
Where the wind plays its symphony,
In concert with the lonesome tree.

The horizon stretches wide,
A canvas brushed with hope,
Each blade of grass a heartbeat,
In the heartbeat of the whole.

- Fanny Buitrago
